text: The Darmstadt University of Technology (; TUD) is a university in Darmstadt, in Germany. It is the largest technical university in the state of Hesse and one of the largest technical universities in Germany with around 25,000 students. == References == ==Other websites== * Official website Category:Darmstadt Category:Colleges and universities in Hesse Category:Technical colleges and universities in Germany Category:1877 establishments in Europe Category:1870s establishments in Germany
